{"tid":748924,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［跪求疹專家］幾年了 唔痕唔痛係乜撚野疹黎","createTime":"2018-07-19T14:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T15:05:58.000Z","uid":78180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a2f0947d2804a06a3c5ccb9ab90236793e59f195","tid":748924,"uid":78180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T14:53:10.000Z","msg":"想當年病發幾個月後 得手臂內側有呢種疹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔痕又唔痛<br />\n去睇左三次醫生 私家又睇過<br />\n都話係唔洗醫既疹or玫瑰糠疹之類<br />\n因為抵抗力低or壓力大之類引起<br />\n幾個月後就自己好番<br />\n你老尾得等左三年都未好番 仲擴散到落隻腳都有<br />\n有冇巴打有類似經歷<br />\n係咪要去驗血<br />\n我都想夏天游水啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/224553_840db79f03ca0a9db3c1be9e547df22d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F224553_840db79f03ca0a9db3c1be9e547df22d.png&h=f3f2680f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/224557_4112fa5b9c425a6a286fc15bfbee7280.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F224557_4112fa5b9c425a6a286fc15bfbee7280.png&h=f9e5d8f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/224559_3e8438cb8ff7644184b84ca48dfa1f0e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F224559_3e8438cb8ff7644184b84ca48dfa1f0e.png&h=bff449b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5f5aabca1cf25b0cacff9f5b8c901534cf376ce","tid":748924,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T14:54:54.000Z","msg":"有冇叫過雞"},{"pid":"0daff6